国伦敦的一位手术助理将微软的 HoloLens 2 头显更换为苹果的 Vision Pro，并将其描述为一次突破性的改变。今年 4 月，我国吉林大学白求恩第三医院成功完成了世界首例应用 Vision Pro 头显辅助的腹腔镜乙状结肠癌根治术；截至今年 5 月据称目前已经有 30 多台外科手术使用苹果 Vision Pro 头显辅助完成。 北大人民医院成功应用苹果 Vision Pro 头显完成肺癌根治术"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-33130b65297f27d553bde196b674a8fd_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/658001572"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI24fYi+rNne19EAMaCTEwODUwMDUzNyDb7/ayBjAAOKYCQAxyCTY1ODAwMTU3MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "13_1717485511.756434", "card_id": "Q_620832838", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 38}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为何总有人强调徐州是四战之地？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "冀州袁绍，兖州曹操以及刘表孙权都没人称它是四战之地。 按实控地盘来看不都是四战之地吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-32f570c6e8471f23b908b10ee6380d60_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "77 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/620832838"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I24fYi+rNne19EAMaCTEwMDI0MjUxOCDctuKnBjAAOEtADXIJNjIwODMyODM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1717485511.756883", "card_id": "Q_658003603", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 24}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2024WTT 重庆冠军赛女单决赛，孙颖莎 4:3 王曼昱获得冠军，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "